  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The breakfast buffet offers an excellent selection of hot and cold dishes and a range of locally-sourced produce.</p>
<p>Complimentary afternoon tea and biscuits is served daily, from 4-5pm.</p>
<p>The evening half board meal is either a three-course buffet or a three-course menu with choice of main.</p>
<p>The hotel's <strong>Stübli</strong> is a Swiss à la carte restaurant with a seasonal menu of local and regional specialities - a great choice for lunch on the terrace.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
