  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms</strong> are around 23m² and sleep two.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> are around 23m² and can sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed). They also have a balcony or terrace and are available for sole occupancy for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are around 30m² and sleep two to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They also have a balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath (with showerhead)</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. CHF 5.50 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged 11 and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Steps into property: <strong>No</strong></li>
<li>Adapted rooms: <strong>Yes</strong></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
